ww.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: So incredibly full of shit I can't even begin...</span><hr size=1> No, I just posted that randomly lol. Got a burr in my saddle this afternoon and saw that and thought it was wildly funny. <br>
