I see nothing inconsistant with enjoying DK and being a conservative; just cuz Jello is a flaming commie doesn't mean he can't make fun music; such lighthearted hits as _Holiday_In_Cambodia_ actually lambast the kind of self-hating middle class white socialist idiots that I deplore. See also Oingo Boingo, _Capitalism_ for more fun New Wave liberal bashing. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
